Example C extension using setuptools.

Various (independent options)

# install package locally
pip install .

# build tgz source distribution in dist/foo-1.tar.gz (no compilation happens)
python setup.py sdist

# test compilation in-place (just the compilation)
python setup.py build

# compile and build a binary package dist/foo-1-XXXXXXXXXX.whl
python setup.py bdist_wheel

# compile and install a tgz source distribution
pip install dist/foo-1.tar.gz

# install from github directly (will compile and install)
pip install "git+https://github.com/mnhrdt/libfoo.git/#subdirectory=with_setuptools"

